<p>The word â€œmini-ikitaiâ€ means â€œto go to seeâ€, and this is formed of words â€œmiruâ€ which means â€œsee/watch/lookâ€ and â€œikitaiâ€ which was described above.</p>
<p>Another useful phrase is â€œmitai desuâ€ which means â€œI want to watchâ€</p>
